## ğŸ“ Static File Handling

```python
# Serve static files
app.static("static/", "/static/")
app.static("uploads/", "/files/")

# Now accessible at:
# /static/style.css -> static/style.css
# /files/document.pdf -> uploads/document.pdf
```

